description: L.A. Roots is a truck born from Latin American influence, with L.A. Flava! This is a new truck from the Aji Mobile Foods Family, and it brings a host of delicious meals, from the "Gaucho" and "Inca" to the "Saltado" or "Hornado," all fantastic combinations of marinated meats and tasty veggies that you can order as a sandwich, tacos, or a bowl! Stop by and grab one of these great meals today!
name: L.A. Roots
